Patch Set 3:

On Tizen:Generic: your submit request was accepted and iniparser built fine.

But a lot of indirect dependencies were broken, usually because of non resolved symbol iniparser_getstr at link time.

Typical example was bluetooth-frwk.

Even if it's tagged accepted in git tree, we reverted to previous version on OBS package. Follow up on PTREL-101.
